org.stanwood.media.util
Class StreamGobbler

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Thread
      org.stanwood.media.util.StreamGobbler
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Runnable
public class StreamGobbler
extends java.lang.Thread

Used to swallow the contents of a stream. This is a thread based class, so Thread.start() should be called to start the thread. getResult() can be called to get the contents of the swallowed stream.
